    <item>
      <title>What Happens to My Photos if I Turn Off iCloud</title>
      <link>https://peoplealsoask.github.io/what-happens-to-my-photos-if-i-turn-off-icloud/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jun 2026 06:20:21 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://peoplealsoask.github.io/what-happens-to-my-photos-if-i-turn-off-icloud/</guid>
      <description>If you turn off iCloud, your photos will be removed from the cloud, but they will still be available on your device. However, if you&amp;rsquo;re using the iCloud Photo Library, your photos might be deleted from your device as well, depending on your device&amp;rsquo;s storage settings.</description>
